erate%20with%20the%20state%20administration%20and%20the%20police.%20%26quot%3BSome%20anti-social%20elements%20hatched%20a%20conspiracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-member%20judicial%20commissioned%2C%20headed%20by%20Allahabad%20High%20Court's%20retired%20judge%2C%20Justice%20Brijesh%20Kumar%20Srivastav%2C%20is%20investigating%20the%20tragedy.%20The%20panel%20is%20likely%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20in%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20judicial%20panel%20probe%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20raised%20a%20big%20question.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20is%20not%20an%20accident%2C%20then%20whose%20conspiracy%20is%20this%3F%20All%20of%20this%20will%20be%20probed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Hathras%2C%20where%20he%20met%20those%20injured%20and%20visited%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20stampede%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20when%20asked%20why%20the%20'godman'%20has%20not%20been%20named%20an%20accused%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPrima%20facie%2C%20the%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20those%20who%20applied%20for%20permission%20for%20the%20event.%20Whoever%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%20will%20come%20under%20its%20purview.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20judicial%20panel%2C%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20led%20by%20Agra's%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Anupam%20Kulshreshtha%20is%20probing%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20announced%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20the%20families%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20stampede.%20Many%20families%2C%20reports%20say%2C%20are%20still%20looking%20for%20their%20own%20who%20attended%20the%20'satsang'.%C2%A0Rajkumari%20Devi%20from%20Unnao%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20only%20the%20poor%20who%20meet%20this%20fate%2C%20not%20the%20rich.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20seate