me%20as%20they%20will%20be%20to%20every%20single%20person%20watching%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Starmer%20told%20reporters%20on%20his%20own%20campaign%20visit.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20increasing%20desperation%20bordering%20on%20hysterical%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conservative%20attacks%2C%20which%20were%20widely%20criticized%20by%20leaders%20in%20Britain's%20Jewish%20community%2C%20come%20despite%20Sunak%20saying%20just%20two%20weeks%20ago%20that%20he%20admired%20Starmer%20for%20ensuring%20he%20has%20family%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20does%20a%20very%20good%20job%20of%20balancing%20family%20life%20and%20work%20life%20and%20making%20sure%20that%20he%20prioritizes%20that%20and%20makes%20time%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sunak%20told%20LBC%20radio%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20by%20Bloomberg%20if%20he%20endorsed%20the%20comments%20by%20his%20campaign%20alleging%20Starmer%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20defend%20the%20country%20because%20he'd%20finish%20work%20at%206%20pm%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20worry%20about%20our%20country's%20security%20under%20Keir%20Starmer%20and%20I%20have%20deep%20concerns%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20overall%20vibe%20is%20of%20a%20campaigning%20running%20out%20of%20ideas%20to%20try%20to%20close%20the%20polling%20gap%20to%20Labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETory%20leaflets%20warn%20of%20%26quot%3BFrench-style%20union%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20national%20road%20charging%20and%20more%20money%20spent%20on%20welfare%20benefits.%20That's%20despite%20Labour%20saying%20changes%20to%20working%20rights%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20in%20communication%20with%20business%2C%20pledging%20to%20get%20people%20off%20benefits%20and%20into%20work%2C%20and%20having%20announced%20no%20plans%20for%20national%20pay-per-mile%20charging%20on%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20BBC%2C%20the%20premier%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3Billegal%20migrants%20will%20be%20out%20on%20the%20street%26quot%3B%20if%20Labour%20wins%2C%20and%20that%20asylum-seekers%20were%20%26quot%3Bqueuing%20up%26quot%3B%20at%20Calais%20in%20northern%20France%2C%20waiting%20for%20a%20Starmer%20government%20before%20attempting%20to%20cross%20the%20English%20Channel%20in%20small%20boats.%20That's%20despite%20the%20Channel%20crossings%20through%20the%20end%20of%20June%20reaching%20a%20record%20for%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabour%20has%20denied%20any%20plan%20to%20raise%20taxes%2C%20insisting%20it%20will%20not%20put%20up%20any%20on%20%26quot%3Bworking%20people%26quot%3B%20and%20categorically%20ruling%20out%20rises%20to%20income%20tax%2C%20the%20national%20insurance%20payroll%20tax%2C%20corporation%20tax%20and%20valued-added%20tax.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20accused%20Mr%20Sunak%20of%20lying%20to%20the%20public%20about%20their%20policies%20on%20borders%20and%20the%20work%20ethic%20of%20their%20would-be%20premier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bstench%20of%20their%20lies%20and%20hypocrisy%26quot%3B%20is%20%26quot%3Boverwhelming%2C%26quot%3B%20Shadow%20Health%20Secretary%20Wes%20Streeting%20said%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWith%20two%20days%20to%20go%2C%20Labour%20is%20setting%20out%20its%20vision%20for%20our%20country's%20future.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Conservatives%20are%20slinging%20mud.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThey%20can't%20tell%20the%20truth%20about%20their%20own%20record%2C%20so%20they%20lie%20about%20Labour's%20plans.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt's%20time%20to%20choose%20change%20and%20bring%20the%20circus%20in%20Downing%20Street%20to%20an%20end.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FI5GpKNzt2d%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FI5GpKNzt2d%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Wes%20Streeting%20(%40wesstreeting)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fwesstreeting%2Fstatus%2F1808062255293976642%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255