da%20keeps%20his%20toppings%20and%20sauce%20simple%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20he%20always%20skips%20the%20lettuce%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELaFrieda%20usually%20pairs%20his%20meat%20with%20just%20a%20small%20dollop%20of%20mayonnaise%20and%20some%20halved%20grape%20tomatoes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20worse%20than%20a%20big%20tomato%20that's%20almost%20like%20a%20watermelon%20and%20has%20no%20flavor%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhereas%20tiny%20grape%20tomatoes%2C%20all%20you%20do%20is%20cut%20them%20in%20half%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20you%20get%20bursts%20of%20flavor.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaFrieda%20said%20he%20prefers%20to%20have%20a%20Caesar%20salad%20on%20the%20side%20instead%20of%20adding%20lettuce%20to%20his%20burger%2C%20and%20he%20usually%20skips%20onions%20because%20they%20can%20%26quot%3Boverpower%20the%20flavor%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blinger%20around%20well%20after.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAnd%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20buns%2C%20LaFrieda%20always%20loves%20brioche%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELaFrieda%20said%20the%20bun%20is%20often%20overlooked%2C%20but%20it's%20crucial%20to%20a%20perfect%20burger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20first%20thing%20you're%20touching%2C%20it's%20the%20first%20thing%20you're%20tasting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can't%20overpower%20the%20burger%2C%20it%20can't%20be%20too%20bready.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrioche%20buns%20are%20LaFrieda's%20favorite%2C%20and%20he%20recommends%20slightly%20warming%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bbring%20magic%20to%20a%20burger.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20a%20fan%20of%20King's%20Hawaiian%20buns%2C%20which%20he%20said%20are%20great%20when%20%26quot%3Byou%20want%20something%20a%20little%20bit%20different.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaFrieda%20doesn't%20have%20any%20special%20tricks%20or%20tips%20to%20make%20the%20perfect%20burger%2C%20but%20he%20says%20that's%20the%20whole%20point.%C2%