0We%20like%20that%20it%20comes%20with%20bolts%20to%20mount%20it%20securely%2C%20and%20it's%20relatively%20affordable%20for%20its%20size.%20Plus%2C%20setting%20the%20keycode%20was%20straightforward.%20It%20isn't%20one%20of%20our%20top%20picks%20because%20it%20isn't%20fireproof%2C%20and%20we%20broke%20into%20it%20within%20two%20minutes%20using%20a%20small%20sledgehammer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EBest%20fireproof%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SentrySafe%20HD4100%20Fireproof%20Safe%20was%20the%20only%20safe%20to%20pass%20our%20water%20and%20fire%20tests.%20The%20safe%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.intertek.com%2Fmarks%2Fetl-verified%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EETL%20verified%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20stay%20waterproof%20when%20submerged%20for%2072%20hours.%20We%20submerged%20the%20safe%20for%2045%20hours%2C%20and%20the%20interior%20remained%20dry.%20It's%20UL%20classified%20as%20fireproof%20when%20exposed%20to%20temperatures%20up%20to%201%2C550%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20for%20half%20an%20hour.%20We%20threw%20the%20safe%20in%20a%20fire%20for%20about%2025%20minutes%2C%20and%20the%20paper%20and%20digital%20media%20we%20put%20inside%20were%20unharmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20destroying%20the%20safe%20in%20the%20fire%20test%2C%20I%20used%20it%20to%20protect%20my%20valuables%20for%20about%20a%20year.%20The%20spacious%20interior%20was%20enough%20for%20my%20important%20files.%20Since%20we%20put%20this%20safe%20through%20the%20fire%20test%2C%20we%20couldn't%20test%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20to%20break%20into%2C%20but%20from%20personal%20experience%2C%20the%20locking%20mechanism%20feels%20flimsy.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SentrySafe%20comes%20with%20two%20keys.%20You%20turn%20the%20key%2C%20lift%20the%20handle%2C%20and%20you're%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20somewhat%20cumbersome%20to%20carry%2C%20a%20motivated%20burglar%20could%20easily%20remove%20the%20safe%20from%20your%20home.%20There%20are%20no%20bolts%20for%20securing%20it.%20I%20kept%20it%20hidden%20in%20an%20air%20fryer%20box%20in%20a%20hard-to-access%20spot%20in%20my%20basement%20to%20keep%20it%20inconspicuous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EBest%20portable%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20you%20don't%20want%20a%20safe%20that%20is%20easy%20to%20move%20because%20it's%20easy%20to%20steal.%20If%20theft%20of%20the%20safe%20isn't%20a%20concern%2C%20the%20SentrySafe%201200%20Fireproof%20Box%20is%20an%20affordable%20way%20to%20transport%20small%20items%20under%20lock%20and%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SentrySafe%20Fireproof%20Box%20is%20UL-classified%20to%20handle%20temperatures%20up%20to%201%2C550%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20for%20half%20an%20hour.%20After%20putting%20it%20in%20a%20fire%20for%20about%2025%20minutes%2C%20the%20papers%2C%20USB%20drive%2C%20and%20microSD%20card%20inside%20remained%20unharmed%2C%20though%20we%20destroyed%20the%20safe.%20It%20isn't%20waterproof%2C%20but%20the%20box's%20contents%20stayed%20dry%20when%20we%20doused%20it%20with%20water%20to%20extinguish%20the%20fire.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safe%20comes%20with%20two%20keys%2C%20the%20only%20way%20to%20open%20it.%20You%20can't%20remove%20the%20key%20while%20it's%20unlocked%2C%20ensuring%20you%20don't%20accidentally%20lock%20the%20keys%20inside.%20The%20safe%20also%20has%20a%20handle%20for%20easy%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20home%20safe%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221430%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20safes%20lay%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20various%20states%20of%20functionality%20after%20being%20pummeled%20with%20a%20hammer%20and%20crowbar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61d35e3487e64b0018e12cae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221073%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20good%20home%20safe%20should%20be%20be%20fireproof%20and%20floodproof%2C%20and%20if%20you'll%20be%20storing%20items%20of%20significant%20value%2C%20it%20should%20be%20heavy%20or%20bolted%20down.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20depends%20on%20what%20you%20want%20to%20safeguard%20and%20what%20you%20are%20protecting%20it%20from.%20If%20you're%20trying%20to%20protect%20important%20documents%20from%20floods%20or%20fires%2C%20you%20can%20get%20by%20with%20a%20smaller%20ETL-verified%20or%20UL-rated%20safe%20to%20protect%20against%20these%20hazards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20have%20larger%20valuables%2C%20including%20rifles%2C%20that%20you%20want%20to%20keep%20safe%20from%20burglars%2C%20you'll%20want%20a%20heavy-duty%20safe.%20John%20Dean%2C%20owner%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deansafe.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDean%20Safe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%2050%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20recommended%20looking%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ul.com%2Fnews%2Fresidential-security-container-standard-revised%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUL%20residential%20security%20container%20(RSC)%20burglary%20rating%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20ensure%20a%20safe%20will%20keep%20your%20valuables%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELouis%20Chavez%2C%20the%20global%20principal%20engineer%20in%20UL's%20Built%20Environment%20group%2C%20outlined%20how%20UL%20tests%20safes%20that%20receive%20RSC%20designation.%20%26quot%3BRSCs%20are%20generally%20used%20in%20residential%20homes%20and%20should%20comply%20with%20UL%201037%2C%20the%20Standard%20for%20Antitheft%20Alarms%20and%20Devices%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20UL%201037%20involves%20using%20hand%20tools%20you'd%20commonly%20find%20in%20the%20home%20to%20attack%20the%20safe%20for%20up%20to%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDean%20also%20recommended%20choosing%20a%20heavy%20safe%20or%20at%20least%20securely%20bolting%20it%20down%20because%20if%20a%20burglar%20can%20remove%20a%20safe%20from%20your%20home%2C%20they%20will%20get%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20we%20test%20safes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221430%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22First%20Alert%202037F%20Water%20and%20Fire%20Protector%20File%20Chest%20are%20set%20ablaze%20in%20a%20fire%20pit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61d35d6699a7690019de7159%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221073%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20lit%20each%20safe%20on%20fire%20to%20test%20fireproof%20claims.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20each%20safe%20in%20this%20guide%20through%20several%20objective%20tests.%20Though%20the%20most%20important%20features%20will%20vary%20based%20on%20your%20situation%2C%20experts%20recommend%20choosing%20a%20fireproof%20safe%20that%20is%20hard%20to%20move%20and%20break%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20attributes%20of%20the%20best%20safes%20and%20how%20we%20tested%20them%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20a%20safe%20is%20light%20enough%20to%20steal%2C%20a%20burglar%20will%20get%20into%20it%2C%20says%20Dean.%20All%20safes%20we%20tested%20were%20relatively%20light.%20The%20heaviest%20was%20only%20about%2042%20pounds.%20We%20gave%20preference%20to%20safes%20that%20came%20with%20bolts%20for%20secure%20mounting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUL%2C%20the%20leading%20safe%20certification%20company%2C%20rates%20residential%20safes%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstandardscatalog.ul.com%2FProductDetail.aspx%3FproductId%3DUL1037%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUL%20Standard%201037%3C%2Fa%3E)%20based%20on%20five%20to%2010%20minutes%20of%20attack%20time%20using%20common%20hand%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20a%20pry%20bar%20and%20hammers.%20We%20used%20a%20small%20pry%20bar%20and%20a%204-pound%20sledgehammer%20to%20breach%20the%20safes%20and%20access%20the%20contents.%20None%20of%20the%20safes%20we%20tested%20took%20more%20than%20five%20minutes%20to%20access.%20We%20rated%20them%20based%20on%20difficulty.%20Our%20top%20pick%20was%20the%20hardest.%20The%20Jssmst%20book%20safe%20was%20the%20easiest%2C%20taking%20my%20seven-year-old%20one%20minute%20to%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFire%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20safes%20we%20tested%20were%20UL%20Class%20350%20half-hour%20rated.%20This%20rating%20means%20that%20when%20the%20safe%20is%20exposed%20to%20temperatures%20of%201%2C550%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20the%20internal%20temp%20won't%20exceed%20350%20degrees%20for%20at%20least%20half%20an%20hour.%20This%20makes%20the%20safe%20suitable%20for%20paper%20products%20but%20not%20digital%20media.%20Still%2C%20we%20put%20paper%20documents%20and%20digital%20media%20in%20the%20UL-rated%20safes%20and%20put%20them%20in%20a%20fire%20for%2025%20minutes.%20We%20then%20removed%20the%20safes%20and%20inspected%20the%20contents.%20Since%20fire%20destroys%20a%20safe%2C%20we%20couldn't%20put%20the%20fire-tested%20safes%20through%20the%20security%20test%20above.%20We'll%20be%20getting%20additional%20samples%20to%20break%20open%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWater%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETwo%20of%20the%20fireproof%20safes%20were%20designated%20as%20waterproof.%20We%20tested%20these%20claims%20by%20putting%20paper%20towels%20and%20a%20magazine%20in%20each%20safe%20and%20submerging%20them%20in%20just%20enough%20water%20to%20cover%20them%20completely.%20We%20checked%20the%20safes%20after%20at%20least%2022%20hours%20to%20see%20if%20the%20contents%20were%20dry.%20Only%20the%20SentrySafe%20HD4100%20remained%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20We%20assessed%20whether%20we%20needed%20instructions%20to%20set%20up%20the%20safe%20and%20whether%20any%20features%20made%20it%20hard%20or%20easy%20to%20use.%20We%20also%20timed%20how%20long%20it%20took%20to%20open%20the%20safes%20using%20each%20available%20method.%20None%20of%20the%20safes%20took%20more%20than%2010%20seconds%20to%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20cite%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40techinsider%2Fvideo%2F7049426435089665326%5C%22%20data-video-id%3D%5C%227049426435089665326%5C%22%3E%20%3Csection%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40techinsider%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%40techinsider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40techinsider%3C%2Fa%3E%20Would%20you%20rather%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ffireproof%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22fireproof%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23fireproof%3C%2Fa%3E%20safe%20or%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fwaterproof%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22waterproof%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23waterproof%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Ftechinsider%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22techinsider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23techinsider%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fsafes%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22safes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23safes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fsafe%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22safe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23safe%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Ftag%2Fathomesafe%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22athomesafe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23athomesafe%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Fmusic%2FUp-and-Away-Vocalese-6777299168986662914%3Frefer%3Dembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%99%AC%20Up%20and%20Away%20(Vocalese)%20-%20GHOSTLAND%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%99%AC%20Up%