f%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famericansecuritysafes.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Security%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20well-known%20brands%20recommended%20by%20experts%20we%20talked%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20you%20get%20the%20most%20out%20of%20your%20safe%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20experts%20we%20talked%20to%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20keeping%20safes%20hidden.%20%26quot%3BCommon%20places%20to%20avoid%2C%20because%20they%20are%20obvious%20to%20burglars%2C%20include%20bedroom%20closets%20and%20bedroom%20dresser%20drawers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chavez.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20recommended%20covering%20your%20safe%20with%20a%20box%20or%20disguising%20it%20as%20a%20bookshelf.%20He%20suggested%20hiding%20wall%20safes%20behind%20a%20picture%20or%20artwork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20also%20cautioned%20against%20using%20obvious%20passcodes.%20%26quot%3BAvoid%20codes%20like%20123456%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hall.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20use%20your%20birthday%2C%20your%20spouse's%20birthday%2C%20or%20your%20child's%20birthday.%20I've%20been%20changing%20combinations%20for%2020%20years%2C%20and%20you'd%20be%20surprised%20by%20how%20many%20people%20have%20their%20safes%20set%20to%20the%20same%20numbers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20choose%20a%20safe%20that%20isn't%20fireproof%20or%20waterproof%20but%20still%20want%20protection%2C%20consider%20getting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_112918_best-small-safe-20%26h%3Da43228bac9b53a73c70f32087ab95ad38c9544767895ff6b6fcb7ddfe4900e78%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f41fbe%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-home-safe%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB08K34LMXP%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20fireproof%20document%20bag%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20bags%20are%20relatively%20inexpensive%20and%20easy%20to%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20o