20Oxford%20University%2C%20said%20in%20the%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20need%20to%20be%20really%20vigilant%20now%20and%20move%20to%20try%20and%20contain%20this%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20in%20this%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20the%20opportunity%20for%20this%20to%20get%20on%20an%20airplane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef566fbb-abea-4b10-aabf-9d64faaf238f%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20mpox%20strain%20spreads%20easily%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMpox%20spreads%20through%20close%20contact%2C%20especially%20skin-to-skin%20contact.%20It%20can%20cause%20flu-like%20symptoms%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmonkeypox-rash-pictures-when-to-get-checked-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epainful%20or%20itchy%20rash%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20develops%20into%20puss-filled%20blisters%2C%20lesions%2C%20and%20eventually%20scabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Monkeypox%20palm%20of%20hands%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6286140f0fdb180018cc1c67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20palms%20of%20a%20monkeypox%20patient%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo.%3Cp%3ECenters%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmonkeypox-man-hospitalized-couldnt-swallow-spit-feared-death-symptoms-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrevious%20strains%20of%20the%20virus%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20had%20limited%20transmission%20abilities.%20The%20clade%20I%20virus%20that's%20long%20circulated%20in%20the%20DRC%20has%20been%20mostly%20associated%20with%20spread%20through%20families%20and%20within%20households%2C%20Land%20said.%20The%20clade%20IIb%20virus%20that%20went%20global%20was%20mostly%20sexually%20transmitted%20and%20mostly%20affected%20men%20who%20have%20sex%20with%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20clade%20Ib%20strain%20seems%20to%20do%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20began%20spreading%20through%20sexual%20transmission%2C%20via%20the%20local%20sex%20work%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20the%20researchers.%20However%2C%20they%20said%20the%20new%20virus%20has%20also%20spread%20within%20households%2C%20between%20mothers%20and%20their%20children%2C%20and%20there%20have%20even%20been%20cases%20of%20person-to-person%20spread%20%3Cem%3Eoutside%3C%2Fem%3E%20households%20and%20without%20sexual%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20worrying%2C%26quot%3B%20Lang%20said.%20That's%20because%20it%20has%20more%20opportunities%20to%20spread%20than%20previous%20strains%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clade%20I%20form%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20from%20which%20the%20new%20strain%20has%20emerged%2C%20is%20also%20more%20deadly%20than%20clade%20II.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fpoxvirus%2Fmpox%2Fabout%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWHO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20outbreaks%20have%20killed%20up%20to%2010%25%20of%20sick%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b8b424dd-af4a-4193-a5ac-002f109faf5a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EResearchers%20only%20see%20'the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20yet%20clear%20just%20how%20deadly%20the%20new%20clade%20Ib%20virus%20is%2C%20because%20researchers%20aren't%20sure%20how%20many%20cases%20there%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeandre%20Murhula%20Masirika%2C%20a%20research%20coordinator%20in%20the%20local%20DRC%20health%20department%2C%20said%20in%20the%20briefing%20that%20they%20had%20identified%20more%20than%20600%20cases%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20severe%20cases%20that%20make%20it%20to%20hospital%2C%20so%20this%20will%20be%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%2C%26quot%3B%20Lang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO's%20technical%20lead%20for%20mpox%2C%20Rosamund%20Lewis%2C%20also%20raised%20the%20alarm%20last%20week%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20critical%20need%20to%20address%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20mpox%20cases%20in%20Africa%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhealthcare-pharmaceuticals%2Fwho-scientists-warn-mpox-strain-congo-2024-06-25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20said%20they%20need%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20virus%20to%20identify%20the%20right%20safety%20measures%20and%20vaccines%20to%20contain%20its%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20first%20carry%20out%20studies%20of%20serology%20and%20immunology%20in%20order%20to%20see%20what%20kind%20of%20vaccination%20we%20can%20propose%2C%26quot%3B%20Murhula%20Masirika%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%2C%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20give%20the%20smallpox%20vaccine%20to%20local%20sex%20workers%20and%20healthcare%20workers%20in%20hopes%20that%20it%20will%20confer%20some%20immunity%20to%20mpox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-monkeypox-mpox-virus-global-outbreak-risk-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720042137000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6685b12c1f0c1cd6d7317e53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-monkeypox-mpox-virus-global-outbreak-risk-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20monkeypox%20strain%20spreads%20mpox%20rash%20in%20new%20ways.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20the%20opportunity%20for%20this%20to%20get%20on%20an%20airplane%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20health%20expert%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmcfalljohnsen%40businessinsider.com%20(Morgan%20McFall-Johnsen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A396%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-monkeypox-mpox-virus-global-outbreak-ris