%20the%20firefighters%20now%20had%20one%20of%20their%20own%20brothers%20to%20save.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20they%20tried%20a%20boat%2C%20but%20it%20immediately%20capsized.%20I%20watched%20as%20Paul%20was%20pulled%20in%20with%20a%20life%20preserver%2C%20Dave%20was%20clipped%20onto%20the%20firefighters'%20rope%2C%20and%20dragged%20in.%20But%20still%2C%20no%20Robbie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20were%20frantically%20running%2C%20yelling%2C%20and%20pointing.%20Loud%20whistles%2C%20loud%20crashing%20waves.%20I%20couldn't%20understand%20what%20was%20said%2C%20I%20couldn't%20see%20what%20was%20happening%20between%20the%20undulating%20waves%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20stop%20looking%20for%20my%20brother%2C%20willing%20him%20to%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20parents%20pulled%20up%2C%20unaware%20of%20our%20family's%20fate.%20One%20firefighter%20was%20also%20lost.%20One%20of%20the%20two%20people%20yelling%20from%20the%20water%20was%20saved%20by%20a%20local%20with%20a%20dinghy%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchild-drowned-mom-started-foundation-teach-water-safety-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20one%20drowned%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20stood%20on%20that%20beach%2C%20telling%20our%20parents%20what%20happened%20as%20we%20continued%20scanning%20the%20water%2C%20still%20hoping%20to%20spot%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20getting%20dark%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20pull%20my%20feet%20out%20of%20the%20wet%20sand%20that%20was%20now%20up%20to%20my%20ankles%2C%20didn't%20want%20to%20turn%20my%20back%20and%20leave%20Robbie%20alone%20in%20the%20dark%20water.%20Shaking%20and%20crying%2C%20we%20helped%20each%20other%20up%20the%20wooden%20steps%20to%20the%20cottage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankful%20for%20the%20copious%20amount%20of%20alcohol%2C%20we%20prescribed%20ourselves%20shots%20of%20whiskey%2C%20hoping%20to%20knock%20ourselves%20out%2C%20to%20stop%20the%20spiraling%20thoughts%2C%20the%20reliving%20of%20the%20day.%20We%20lit%20sparklers%20and%20shared%20stories.%20I%20told%20them%20about%20the%20game%20Robbie%20and%20I%20made%20up%20called%20%26quot%3Bdial-a-shot.%26quot%3B%20He%20used%20to%20call%20me%20in%20my%20dorm%20and%20we%20would%20do%20a%20shot%20of%20vodka%20together%20over%20the%20phone%20before%20we%20went%20out.%20We%20held%20our%20glasses%20high%20and%20toasted%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20waited%20for%20the%20effects%20to%20kick%20in%2C%20my%20mind%20dove%20into%20my%20childhood.%20I%20remembered%20when%20Robbie%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20play%20poker.%20I%20remembered%20when%20he%20slipped%20headphones%20on%20my%20ears%20and%20pressed%20play%20so%20I%20could%20hear%20a%20new%20punk%20band%20he%20bought%20on%20cassette.%20I%20saw%20him%20holding%20a%20sci-fi%20paperback%2C%20smoking%20cigarettes%20and%20weed.%20In%20our%20conservative%20Irish%20Catholic%20family%2C%20we%20were%20both%20non-conforming%20weirdos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20waited%20for%20three%20days%2C%20floating%20in%20suspended%20disbelief%2C%20while%20they%20dragged%20the%20lake.%20His%20body%20was%20recovered%20by%20a%20scuba%20diver%20200%20yards%20in%20front%20of%20the%20cottage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce1986bd-4489-49a3-ab3d-35297ba4567b%5C%22%3EI%20still%20dread%20the%20Fourth%20of%20July%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20funeral%2C%20I%20had%20to%20return%20to%20school%2C%20but%20how%20could%20I%20go%20back%20to%20my%20regular%20life%20after%20I%20saw%20my%20brother%20die%3F%20School%20didn't%20feel%20important%20anymore.%20Stressing%20about%20grades%20seemed%20ridiculous.%20In%20our%20small%20town%2C%20everyone%20knew%20our%20big%20family.%20I%20thought%20leaving%20would%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20leaving%20Robbie%20behind%2C%20forgetting%20about%20him%20to%20focus%20on%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchool%20ended%20up%20being%20a%20reprieve%20because%20there%2C%20no%20one%20knew%20my%20family%20was%20one%20less.%20I%20could%20decide%20who%20I%20wanted%20to%20share%20the%20tragedy%20with%2C%20I%20could%20process%20it%20on%20my%20own.%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20witness%20my%20parents%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%20my%20graduation%2C%20Paul%20and%20I%20went%20out%20drinking%20and%20dancing%20and%20toasted%20Robbie%20again%20%E2%80%94%20he%20would%20have%20laughed%20at%20me%20for%20being%20so%20hungover%20when%20I%20walked%20across%20the%20stage%20for%20my%20diploma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobbie%20would%20be%2060%20now.%20I%20still%20cover%20my%20eyes%20during%20movie%20drowning%20scenes.%20I%20panic%20when%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-seal-explains-how-to-survive-a-drowning-attempt-2015-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eson%20goes%20swimming%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20river.%20As%20the%20Fourth%20of%20July%20approaches%20again%2C%20I%20fear%20the%20dreaded%20question%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20want%20to%20watch%20the%20fireworks%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbsolutely%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrother-died-on-fourth-of-july-grief-anniversary-death-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720041126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c65c2e079049018192c7d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrother-died-on-fourth-of-july-grief-anniversary-death-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20family%20had%20a%20reunion%20on%20the%20Fourth%20of%20July%20in%201990%2C%20and%20my%20brother%20drowned.%20Ever%20since%20he%20died%2C%20I've%20dreaded%20the%20holiday%2C%20and%20don't%20celebrate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Janet%20Funk%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A131%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrother-died-on-fourth-of-july-grief-anniversary-death-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20the%20ways%20Donald%20Trump%20wins