quot%3BIf%20you're%20cooking%20for%20a%20big%20group%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20want%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20grill%20and%20get%20that%20temperature%20up%20to%20high%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20consistently%20delivering%20great-tasting%20burgers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESeason%20one%20side%20of%20your%20patty%20before%20grilling%20it%2C%20and%20then%20season%20the%20other%20side%20once%20the%20burger%20is%20on%20the%20grill.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221455%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20peppering%20burgers%20while%20frying%20them%20in%20the%20restaurant%20kitchen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6685741b1f0c1cd6d731453b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221091%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChef%20peppering%20burgers%20while%20frying%20them%20in%20the%20restaurant%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EGuillermo%20Spelucin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20put%20the%20meat%20on%20the%20grill%2C%20season%20the%20side%20of%20the%20burger%20that%20is%20going%20face%20down%2C%20he%20said.%20Once%20it's%20on%20the%20grill%2C%20season%20the%20top%20of%20the%20burger%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20often%20don't%20season%20their%20burgers%20enough%2C%20either.%20You%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20has%20good%20flavor%2C%20which%20comes%20from%20both%20the%20fat%20and%20the%20seasoning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20it%20will%20inevitably%20melt%20off%20on%20the%20grill%2C%20so%20use%20an%20ample%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20Paquette%20added%2C%20saying%20that%20Chili's%20cooks%20use%20four%20%26quot%3Bshakes%26quot%3B%20of%20seasoning%20on%20each%20side%20of%20the%20burger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20the%20burger%20is%20on%20the%20grill%2C%20turn%20the%20temperature%20down%20to%20medium.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221732%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20brown%20burgers%20with%20grill%20marks%20on%20them%20sit%20on%20a%2