e%20UK%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20shore%20up%20Labour%20support%20and%20warn%20against%20complacency%20in%20the%20campaign's%20final%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20change%2C%20you%20have%20to%20vote%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Carmarthenshire%2C%20south%20Wales%2C%20where%20supporters%20handed%20out%20cakes%20with%20red%20ribbons%2C%20the%20colour%20associated%20with%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20taking%20anything%20for%20granted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20before%20flying%20to%20Scotland%20on%20the%20same%20plane%20that%20took%20the%20England%20football%20team%20to%20the%20European%20Championships%20in%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%2C%2044%2C%20sought%20to%20hammer%20home%20his%20oft-repeated%20warnings%20that%20a%20Labour%20government%20would%20mean%20tax%20rises%20and%20weaker%20national%20security%20--%20jibes%20that%20Labour%20has%20branded%20a%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20cling%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tories%20also%20stepped%20up%20their%20warnings%20to%20voters%20to%20stop%20the%20prospect%20of%20Labour%20winning%20a%20%26quot%3Bsupermajority%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20Labour%20fears%20is%20intended%20to%20hit%20turnout.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%20ally%20Mel%20Stride%2C%20the%20work%20and%20pensions%20secretary%2C%20said%20Wednesday%20the%20electorate%20would%20%26quot%3Bregret%26quot%3B%20handing%20Labour%20%26quot%3Buntrammelled%26quot%3B%20power%20without%20an%20effective%20Tory%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20Bigger%20than%20Blair%3F%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20polls%2C%20it%20is%20pretty%20clear%20that%20Labour%20at%20this%20stage%20are%20heading%20for%20an%20extraordinary%20landslide%20on%20a%20scale%20that%20has%20probably%20never%2C%20ever%20been%20seen%20in%20this%20country%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20right-wing%20broadcaster%20GB%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20ex-PM%20Bori