-cancelled-for-team-india-aviation-watchdog-seeks-report-from-air-india-6026638%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'5-Star'%20Ashram%20On%20Land%20Worth%204%20Crores%3A%20Documents%20Detail%20Bhole%20Baba's%20Wealth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20stampede%20in%20Hathras%20in%20which%20121%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20most%20of%20them%20women%2C%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%2C%20more%20details%20are%20coming%20out%20about%20the%20self-styled%20godman%2C%20Bhole%20Baba%20aka%20Narayan%20Saakar%20Hari%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20tragedy.%20Within%20hours%20of%20the%20revelation%20that%20the%20guru%20had%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20against%20him%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20they%20have%20seized%20documents%20detailing%20a%20portion%20of%20his%20immense%20wealth%2C%20including%20a%2013-acre%20%26quot%3Bfive-star%26quot%3B%20ashram%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Mainpuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20of%20the%20ashram%20alone%20is%20valued%20at%20Rs%204%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20show%20that%20Mainpuri%20ashram%2C%20spread%20over%2021%20bighas%2C%20has%20several%20rooms%2C%20all%20of%20which%20have%20amenities%20akin%20to%20those%20at%20a%20five-star%20hotel.%20The%20'godman'%2C%20whose%20original%20name%20is%20Suraj%20Pal%2C%20has%20not%20been%20named%20in%20the%20lone%20case%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20stampede%20and%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20living%20in%20the%20ashram%2C%20where%20six%20rooms%20are%20earmarked%20for%20him.%20Another%20six%20rooms%20are%20set%20aside%20for%20committee%20members%20and%20volunteers%20in%20his%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20luxurious%20facilities%20don't%20end%20there.%20Not%20only%20does%20the%20ashram%20have%20a%20private%20road%20but%20also%20a%20state-of-the-art%20cafeteria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPal%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20land%20for%20the%20ashram%20was%20gifted%20to%20him%20three%20to%20four%20years%20ago%20but%20the%20documents%20reveal%20that%20he%20has%20several%20other%20properties%20worth%20crores.%20Many%20of%20these%20properties%20are%20ashrams%20in%20other%20places%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Anti-Social%20Elements'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETuesday's%20stampede%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20121%20people%2C%20including%20at%20least%20seven%20children%2C%20occurred%20at%20a%20'satsang'%20(religious%20event)%20organised%20by%20Pal%20and%20his%20organisation%20in%20Phulrai%20village%20under%20Sikandra%20Rao%20police%20station%20limits%20in%20Hathras.%20Police%20said%20permission%20had%20been%20given%20for%2080%2C000%20people%20but%202.5%20lakh%20had%20gathered%20for%20the%20event.%20When%20Pal%20was%20leaving%20in%20his%20car%2C%20a%20crowd%20rushed%20to%20collect%20the%20dust%20left%20in%20its%20wake%2C%20thinking%20of%20it%20as%20a%20blessing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20control%20the%20crowd%2C%20the%20volunteers%20and%20others%20in%20charge%20of%20security%20from%20Pal's%20organisation%2C%20began%20pushing%20people%20back.%20Several%20devotees%20fell%20around%20an%20embankment%20and%20were%20crushed%20by%20the%20crowd.%20Amid%20the%20chaos%2C%20other%20attendees%20began%20running%2C%20triggering%20a%20stampede.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIssuing%20a%20brief%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%20after%20maintaining%20silence%20since%20the%20stampede%2C%20Pal%20expressed%20his%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims%20and%20said%20he%20will%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20%26quot%3Banti-social%20elements%26quot%3B%20that%20were%20allegedly%20behind%20the%20tragedy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20to%20some%20of%20the%20witnesses...%20they%20said%20that%20during%20the%20'satsang'%2C%20when%20women%20wanted%20to%20touch%20the%20godman's%20feet%2C%20a%20sea%20of%20people%20pushed%20forward%20and%20his%20security%20pushed%