tidiabetic%20properties%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJackfruit%20helps%20strengthen%20bones%2C%20prevents%20bone-related%20disorders%20like%20osteoporosis%2C%20anaemia%2C%20aids%20blood%20circulation%2C%20and%20supports%20thyroid%20gland%20metabolism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20grow%20this%20superfood%20at%20home%2C%20we%20have%20got%20you%20covered!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELucknow-based%20urban%20gardener%20Abhijeet%20Prajapati%2C%20who%20has%20been%20growing%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20on%20his%20terrace%20for%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20shares%20tips%20on%20how%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F244522%2Fmaharashtra-konkan-farmer-jackfruit-trees-varieties-sapling-nursery-buy-ratnagiri%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivate%20jackfruit%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20grow%20jackfruit%20in%20an%20open%20space%20of%20your%20house.%20But%20if%20you%20lack%20open%20space%2C%20you%20can%20still%20harvest%20jackfruit%20by%20growing%20its%20tree%20in%20a%20big%20container%20or%20a%20grow%20bag%20on%20the%20terrace%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijeet%20says%20that%20jackfruit%20can%20be%20planted%20from%20seeds%2C%20cuttings%20or%20saplings%20bought%20from%20the%20nursery.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20when%20planted%20from%20seeds%2C%20it%20may%20take%20about%20seven%20years%20for%20it%20to%20bear%20fruit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20you%20bring%20a%20grafted%20plant%20from%20the%20nursery%20and%20plant%20it%2C%20you%20will%20start%20getting%20fruits%20in%20about%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20takes%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20your%20plant%20starts%20growing.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fjackfruit-1-1719926465-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355176%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20takes%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20before%20your%20plant%20starts%20growing.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHe%20shares%2010%20tips%20to%20grow%20jackfruit%20on%20the%20terrace%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETake%20a%20big%2C%20strong%20container%20like%20a%20drum%20or%20a%20grow%20bag%20with%20a%20good%20drainage%20system.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFill%20this%20container%20with%20the%20potting%20mix.%20To%20prepare%20potting%20mix%2C%20combine%20soil%20and%20cow%20dung%20in%20a%207%3A3%20ratio.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20ideal%20time%20for%20planting%20is%20June%20to%20August.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBuy%20a%20healthy%20ripened%20jackfruit%20from%20the%20market%20and%20sow%20its%20seeds.%20In%20place%20of%20seeds%2C%20you%20can%20also%20directly%20plant%20its%20sapling%20in%20the%20container.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20seeds%20germinate%20in%20about%20a%20week%20but%20the%20cuttings%20may%20take%20more%20than%20a%20month%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJackfruit%20trees%20need%20ample%20sunlight.%20Ensure%20the%20plant%20is%20positioned%20where%20it%20can%20receive%20at%20least%20six%20t