s%20%E2%80%98hope%20in%20human%20form%E2%80%99%20for%20her%20patients%20at%20the%20Civil%20Hospital%2C%20Ahmedabad%3B%20they%20see%20her%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life%2C%20heralding%20her%20a%20miracle%20worker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESakshi%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20this%20feeling.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20only%20seven%20years%20ago%20that%20she%20looked%20at%20her%20surgeons%20through%20the%20same%20lens%20when%20she%20spent%20months%20at%20the%20Manipal%20Hospital%20after%20a%20life-threatening%20accident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20sits%20down%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20recall%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20toughest%20phases%20of%20her%20life%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20finds%20it%20almost%20impossible%20to%20relive%20the%20details.%20This%20is%20due%20to%20two%20reasons%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20Sakshi%20was%20unconscious%20for%2020%20days%20and%20the%20things%20she%20does%20remember%20are%20almost%20too%20painful%20to%20reminisce%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20time%20Sakshi%20revisits%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F249129%2Fsanjay-dubey-pizza-pasta-accident-up-delhi-food-stall-entrepreneur-artificial-limb-inspirational-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20incident%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20her%20carefree%20life%20before%20it%2C%20it%20is%20almost%20like%20knocking%20on%20an%20old%20friend%E2%80%99s%20door%2C%20but%20one%20who%20isn%E2%80%99t%20home%20anymore.%20You%20see%2C%20a%20new%20Sakshi%20was%20reborn%20following%20the%20accident%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Sakshi%202.0%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20her%20mother%20calls%20it%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20and%20this%20version%20is%20here%20to%20stay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20from%20being%20a%20second-year%20MBBS%20student%20who%20met%20with%20a%20horrifying%20accident%20leaving%20her%20with%20multiple%20broken%20bones%20to