20fertility).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experimenting%20and%20researching%20over%20the%20weekends%20between%202019%20and%202021%2C%20Smarika%20took%20the%20plunge%20into%20full-time%20farming.%20With%20seeds%20purchased%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20the%20Chandrakar%20family%20prepared%20for%20their%20first%20tomato%20harvest%20in%202021.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20a%20great%20harvest%20of%20almost%2050%20tonnes%20per%20acre%20in%20the%20first%20year.%20We%20sold%20it%20in%20local%20%3Cem%3Emandis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marts)%20and%20in%20other%20cities%20like%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Patna%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20more.%20I%20have%20tied-up%20with%20brokers%20with%20whom%20I%20pre-decide%20the%20rates%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20tomatoes%2C%20she%20also%20grows%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20cucumber%20and%20brinjal.%20The%20sowing%20and%20harvesting%20season%20is%20between%20May%20to%20March%2C%20with%20the%20cycle%20roughly%20around%20three%20months%2C%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20would%20only%20be%20able%20to%20harvest%20paddy%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20harvest%20vegetables%20many%20more%20times.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20much%20more%20profitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20Dilip%20Rajan%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20a%20thousand%20square%20metres%20of%20land%20planted%20with%20bitter%20gourd%20will%20give%20a%20farmer%20roughly%20the%20same%20income%20as%20one%20hectare%20planted%20for%20rice.%20Vegetables%20can%20be%20harvested%20quickly%20(45-55%20days)%2C%20and%203-4%20crops%20can%20be%20cultivated%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20meet%20the%20increased%20demand%20for%20vegetables%20and%20changes%20in%20food%20consumption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFarming%20is%20a%20viable%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%5C