r-inspiring-senior-citizen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarbie%20dolls%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20created%20a%20certain%20beauty%20standard%2C%20for%20example%20an%20image%20of%20certain%20figure%2C%20pointy%20nose%2C%20and%20certain%20colour.%20This%20created%20wrong%20notions%20in%20children%E2%80%99s%20minds.%20We%20also%20want%20to%20change%20this%20concept.%20We%20promote%20body%20positivity%2C%20various%20colours%20and%20skin%20tones.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20is%20through%20these%20dolls%20that%20children%20learn%20about%20beauty%20standards%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20year%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20able%20to%20expand%20the%20work%20in%20B2B%20and%20made%20their%20presence%20across%2060%20offline%20stores%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Goa%2C%20Ooty%2C%20and%20Coonor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20they%20sell%203%2C000%20fabric%20dolls.%20Last%20financial%20year%2C%20they%20clocked%20in%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%2075%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20glad%20that%20with%20this%20work%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20impart%20new%20skills%20and%20ensure%20monetary%20benefits%20for%20tribal%20women.%20The%20cycle%20is%20complete%20only%20when%20women%20start%20making%20money%20out%20of%20it%2C%20and%20do%20not%20practise%20craft%20just%20as%20a%20hobby%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20most%20of%20our%20women%20have%20increased%20their%20monthly%20incomes%20from%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%208-10%2C000.%20Years%20back%20when%20we%20moved%20to%20the%20Nilgiris%2C%20we%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20hoped%20to%20bring%20this%20change.%20There%20is%20nothing%20more%20satisfying%20than%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sunita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Suhas%20Ramegowda.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719494228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-2-1